{"books":[{"id":"whb","name":"文汇报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"见了毛主席心里更亮堂","authors":["莫世狄"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":12,"day":30}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"广西【僮族】　莫世狄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"初开的花朵见了阳光更鲜艳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"僮家的儿女见了毛主席心里更亮堂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的眼睛闪耀着灿烂的曙光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这曙光照耀着人们走向共产主义的天堂!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你那智慧的手指，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指引着全国人民前进的方向。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们永远沿着你指出的方向，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"努力建设共产主义的天堂。"}],"comments":[],"origin":"","comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}